	"system": {
		"description": "<p>Salvia grows to over three feet high, has large leaves, hollow square stems, and sporadic white flowers with violet sepals. It has a long and continuous tradition of religious use to facilitate visionary states of consciousness during spiritual healing sessions.</p>\n<p><em><strong>Effect.</strong></em> When smoked, chewed, or consumed in a tea, salvia grants inspiration to the imbiber. Further, this allows the user to store an additional inspiration. This \"extra slot\" lasts until the consumer’s next long rest.</p>",
